== 製作 ==
2019年10月，[[米高梅|米高梅]]在《[[阿達一族_(2019年電影)|阿達一族]]》的首映週末獲得成功後宣佈製作續集，並定於2021年10月22日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/addams-family-2-in-works-fall-2021-release-1202760482/|title=‘The Addams Family 2’ Is In The Works After Great $35M+ 4-Day Weekend, MGM/UAR Set Fall 2021 Release|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-10-15|accessdate=2020-10-08|archive-date=2019-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191015161717/https://deadline.com/2019/10/addams-family-2-in-works-fall-2021-release-1202760482/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而{{le|康拉德·威儂|Conrad Vernon}}和{{le|格雷格·帝爾南|Greg Tiernan}}將回歸執導電影<ref>{{cite web|last=Ridgely|first=Charlie|url=https://comicbook.com/movies/news/addams-family-sequel-hopes-directors-interview/|title=The Addams Family Directors Explain Their Approach to the Upcoming Sequel|publisher=Comicbook.com|date=2019-11-06|accessdate=2020-10-08|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123201113/https://comicbook.com/movies/news/addams-family-sequel-hopes-directors-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年10月，宣佈[[莎莉·賽隆|莎莉·賽隆]]、[[奧斯卡·伊薩克|奧斯卡·伊薩克]]、[[克蘿伊·摩蕾茲|克蘿伊·摩蕾茲]]、{{le|尼克·克羅爾|Nick Kroll}}、[[貝蒂·蜜勒|貝蒂·蜜勒]]和[[史努比狗狗|史努比狗狗]]回歸聲演電影，並宣佈[[比爾·哈德|比爾·哈德]]加盟配音陣容，而雅沃·沃爾頓將取替[[芬恩·沃夫哈德|芬恩·沃夫哈德]]成為{{le|普斯利·阿達|Pugsley Addams}}的配音員，帝爾南將單獨執導電影<ref name="2020Oct">{{cite web|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|url=https://deadline.com/2020/10/the-addams-family-2-bill-hader-javon-wanna-walton-join-voice-cast-1234593614/|title=‘The Addams Family 2’: Bill Hader & Javon “Wanna” Walton Join Voice Cast|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2020-10-08|accessdate=2020-10-08|archive-date=2020-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008162155/https://deadline.com/2020/10/the-addams-family-2-bill-hader-javon-wanna-walton-join-voice-cast-1234593614/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《阿達一族2》由[[聯美|聯美]]負責北美發行，國際則由[[環球影業|環球影業]]負責發行，並定於2021年10月22日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|last=McNary|first=Dave|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/the-addams-family-sequel-release-2021-1203371333/|title=‘The Addams Family’ Sequel in the Works With 2021 Release Date|publisher=[[Variety|Variety]]|date=2019-10-15|accessdate=2020-10-08|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812124106/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/the-addams-family-sequel-release-2021-1203371333/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年10月，電影提前至2021年10月8日在美國上映<ref name="2020Oct" />。2021年1月，電影提前至2021年10月1日在美國上映<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/james-bond-pic-no-time-to-die-delays-release-to-fall/ |title=James Bond: 'No Time To Die' Release Date Delayed to Fall |first=Pamela |last=McClintock |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2021-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210604005234/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/james-bond-pic-no-time-to-die-delays-release-to-fall-4115187/ |archive-date=2021-06-04 |url-status=live |access-date=2021-01-22}}</ref>。
=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據111條評論，本片獲得28%的新鮮度，平均得分4.6／10，觀眾投票獲得69%的分數，平均得分為3.8／5<ref>{{Cite Rotten Tomatoes|title=The Addams Family 2 |id=the_addams_family_2|type=movie|access-date=2021-10-01}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影獲得37分<ref>{{Cite Metacritic|id=the-addams-family-2|type=movie|title=The Addams Family 2 |access-date=2021-10-01}}</ref>。

